      • nodeHasLabel

        boolean nodeHasLabel(long nodeId,
                   long labelId)
                     throws EntityNotFoundException
        Checks if a node is labeled with a certain label or not. Returns true if the node is labeled with the label, otherwise false. Label ids are retrieved from KeyWriteOperations.labelGetOrCreateForName(String) or KeyReadOperations.labelGetForName(String).
        Throws:
        EntityNotFoundException
